summary: An ordinance relating to the collection and disbursement to the Washington State Department of Revenue of the leasehold excise tax on the act or privilege of occupying or using City-owned real or personal property for private use, pursuant to chapter 61, Laws of 1975-76, Second Extraordinary Session, and Ordinance 105450 and the Agreement known as Exhibit An Ordinance relating to thereto; making reimbursement appropriations from the Emergency Fund therefor; and ratifying and confirming prior acts.
